               <note type="description">Treatise on creation of spirits, Pen, Throne, the heavens and ranks of angels. Books mentioned in text are K. al-Nikāḥ (RG 544), K. al-Nafs (RG 521?) and al-Durra al-bayḍāʾ.</note>
               <note type="biblioComments">OY cites four mss., all of them late. According to him, the preface is identical to ʿUqlat al-mustawfiz (RG802) but the end differs – our preliminary inspection indicates that the beginning is a variant, and it goes up to end of chapter on falak al-kawākib, with an extra piece at the end. Similar in content to Chapter 7 in FM. Needs some further research to determine whether this is really an independent work.</note>
